ut a memory, except for the strange visions she keeps having and the fact that she is left with her psychic abilities (i wont call these powers, because people would tend to believe ashe is evil).<br><br>This also would explain why she has no parents, and also why her little brother Tommy still moans about her death in a chopper accident.<br><br>Before she died she was taking one of the chopper tours throughout Tokyo, and something went wrong inside the chopper and it crashed, killing everybody inside.<br><br>---<br><br>As you can see this will become a very complex story, with lots of twists and turns...<br>I will need a psychology study in order to write a story like this^^<br><br>Tell me what you think of the concept too ^^<br><br>-Davy<br><br>BTW Im still having thoughts about her having a split personality, but if it makes the story far too complex, just give a yell! <p><i>"I am known as Valentinez Alcelanella Sihat Sushiraboheretz......Gandigobella Blustradavali Calentrince Pierre André Chark Tenhemo Biholovinci Baldos George Doitzel Kaiser the third........don't hasitate to call!"</i> - <u>Vash</u> <u>the</u> <u>Stampede</u> / <u>Humanoid</u> <u>Typhoon</u> / <u>$$60</u> <u>billion</u> <u>man</u> - <b>Trigun</b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/ugeminigodo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>GeminiGodo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Pre-Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(2/13/02 1:58:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1384.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://website.lineone.net/~sdavis/Graphics/GoredoBio.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_thumbsup.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Concept story.. involves god and an (ex-)angel...</span><hr size=1> Sou