ttp://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1384.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.undeadart.com/forum/alucard.gif width=100 height=94></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_thumbsup.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Concept story.. involves god and an (ex-)angel...</span><hr size=1> I doubt it, and even if they will, you shouldn't worry about it. It's pretty much impossible to make something that won't offend anyone. <p><table width=100% border=0><tr><td>Thomas Bonvillain<br><img src=http://www.undeadart.com/temp/banner/banner.gif><a href=http://www.undeadart.com>undeadart.com</a></td><td><a href=http://pkimage.dhs.org/crit/crit.htm>Click here</a> for a broken link!<br><br></td><tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/uascendedbob.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ascended Bob</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(2/14/02 2:19:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1384.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_thumbsup.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Concept story.. involves god and an (ex-)angel...</span><hr size=1> Well, no arguing with that logic. <br><br>Back to the story though, will there be any kind of conflict? She doesn't have to fight badguys or anything like that its just that most stories have some kind of conflict to be resolved in the end. Perhaps people find out about her powers? Or they find out what she used to be. Even if she just struggles to make sense of her world, that could be called conflict. To me the problems the main character faces make the story much more interesting.<br> <br>But you've got to think the entire thing through. You probably <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> will</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> need to do a psycology study. This poses a great challenge to you. You have to be able to beleivably portray how your character acts, and this just gets harder as you add elements that affect them on that level. I wish you luck. Just remember that you should already know every single thought of your character before you even write a single word.  <p>It takes a big man to cry.It takes an even bigger manto laugh at that man.- Jack Handey</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showPrevMessage?topicID=1384.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showNextMessage?topicID=1384.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1384.topic&index=6><img src=http://www.polykarbon.com/bbsimage/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.emailToFriend?topicID=1384.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.threadControl?topicID=1384.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1384.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1384.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td 